.com/en/apple/ipad?currency=usd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nukeni.com%2Fen%2Fapple%2Fipad%3Fcurrency%3Dusd&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClndB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=a656ea00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nukeni.com/en/apple/ipad?currency=usd</a>"},{"pid":"237b6cdb84b3fc1086b2dfce0ed2fce79c86a065","tid":2499084,"uid":36073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:16:18.000Z","msg":"實際上Cellular 版 iPad Pro 香港售價全球最平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\niPad Pro 11-inch Wi-Fi + Cellular<br />\n<br />\n128GB<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong $966.00</strong><br />\nUnited States $999.00<br />\n<br />\n256GB<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong $1,069.06</strong><br />\nUnited States $1,099.00<br />\n<br />\n512GB<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong $1,275.16</strong><br />\nUnited States $1,299.00<br />\n<br />\n1TB<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong $1,687.38</strong><br />\nUnited States $1,699.00<br />\n<br />\niPad Pro 12.9-inch Wi-Fi + Cellular<br />\n<br />\n128GB<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong $1,275.16</strong><br />\nUnited States $1,299.00<br />\n<br />\n256GB<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong $1,378.22</strong><br />\nUnited States $1,399.00<br />\n<br />\n512GB<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong $1,584.33</strong><br />\nUnited States $1,599.00<br />\n<br />\n1TB<br />\n<strong>Hong Kong $1,996.55</strong><br />\nUnited States $1,999.00<br />\n<br />\nSource :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nukeni.com/en/apple/ipad?currency=usd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nukeni.com%2Fen%2Fapple%2Fipad%3Fcurrency%3Dusd&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClndB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=a656ea00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nukeni.com/en/apple/ipad?currency=usd</a>"},{"pid":"354d30c0fbdfb6e67b6c00f59bb28fffcb66dcee","tid":2499084,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:19:42.000Z","msg":"點解仲平過美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"